'''nette''' in [[Telerin]] means 'sister' (diminutive). It is also a play-name for the ring finger.<ref>{{VT|47}}</ref><ref>{{VT|48}}</ref>

A diminutive form was also ''[[nettice]]''
==Etymology==
From [[PQ]] *''netthi'', [[Sundocarmë|Root]] [[NETH]]
